en (shaman mobs) because they buff him up reeeeeeaaaaal nicely so you will need to dispell him first<P><P>------------------<BR><A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=12024" TARGET=_blank>Panteroo Mcgillakudy</A><BR>High Priest of Fennin Ro</FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#dedfdf"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Valya</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Sarnak Headguard  +15 AC +2 Wis +10 vsMg +11 HP +5.00 Wt   <P>Supposedly drops off the Kly, I bought mine long ago. Have not seen too many people mention it.  It is the standard silver plate look.</FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#f7f7f7"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">grubbleCT</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Depending on your server's market, the root helm from CT has decent stats and a nice clicked effect.</FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#dedfdf"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Jubal</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">I used Velium Spiked Skull Helm for a while, very satisfied with it, nice stats all around, zero weight and best of all, no ugly helm graphic!<P>Now that I think about it, I haven't had an ugly helm graphic in a while and I guess I will never have one again. Here's my helm upgrade path:<P>Velium Spiked Skull Helm (ToFS)<BR>Crown of Hatred (PoH 2nd floor)<BR>Truesight Helm (current, Lendidara the Keeper)<BR>Halo of the Enlightened (will be mine soon, we're on a farm CT spree yay)<P>In summary I'd just like to say:<P>Down with ugly helm graphics!!!</FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#f7f7f7"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Panteroo</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Yes Jubal but.... <P>but.....<P>GNOMES HAVE GOGGLES ! Goggles > all other helms</FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#dedfdf"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Ariyes</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">lvl 60 cleric eh?<P>Thats easy, get to know a really nice crew 